sources.title: La Supplente Va In Citta, 1979
sources.description: Woman gets jilted by her boyfriend so she accuses him of rape, he gets sent to jail, she goes off to be a maid and then a clerk in a store. She gets married and then gets pregnant by her ex once he is out of jail. Ah, love Italian style.Â  Could not find any subtitles for this one.
